{"word":"ἐκπαίω","slug":"ἐκπαίω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκπαίω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-παιήσω</el>) (aor1 <el>ἐξ-έπαισα</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>like <a href='S:ἐκβάλλω'><el>ἐκβάλλω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to throw out of</i> a thing, <i>dash</i> one <i>from</i> it, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to dash out, escape</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}